WEBVTT

01:17:48.233 --> 01:17:49.358
Two more months left, sir.

01:17:49.691 --> 01:17:50.691
Where's Saritha now?

01:17:50.899 --> 01:17:52.024
She's in Kalpetta, sir.

01:17:53.191 --> 01:17:54.358
What are you doing here?

01:17:54.483 --> 01:17:56.108
I came to tell you something, sir.

01:17:56.108 --> 01:17:57.108
Go on.
